criteria.driver_alignment:
Represent — mapped $90B across financials and compared five alternatives;  
Implement — ran code/scenario comparison and visualizations (EPS, leverage shifts);  
Validate — discussed stakeholder preferences and alignment with scenarios.

Represent — defined concrete visualization and scenario plan ("we want to visualize how the $90 billion moves through the financial statements");  
